com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.connective

Class ResultSetUnion<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.ResultSet<O>
      • com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.connective.ResultSetUnion<O>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<O>

    public class ResultSetUnion<O>
extends ResultSet<O>
    A ResultSet which provides a view onto the union of other ResultSets, with deduplication.

    This is equivalent to UNION in SQL terminology, i.e. duplicates are eliminated.

    Author:
    Niall Gallagher
